<hymn_number>24</hymn_number>
<title>Bethlehem Kawl Eng</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Vanmang vawnchawih hung pien ni lenkawl ah,
 Ahung eng tai Bethlehem tang ah;
 Gitloh zanthima suihlung mawlte di'n,
 I chung lenkawl ni a hung suok tai.

[V2]
 Lampak hitiu chamna Lal vawnchawih,
 Kumsawt tawplo Lal lai vul zel ding;
 Sietlei leh thangvan ah lal tan tin,
 A gamin tawpni him nei puona.

[V3]
 2. Chung si-al saktieng kawlah ngobang lang,
 Zingzin michingten sul a zui ui;
 Thangvan mithiengten simlei gal dawtin,
 Chun lieng vawnsen naubang a awi ui.

[V4]
 3. Vanmang vawnchawih pienna dai bawng In ah,
 Chieh in aw Lautha sing va lawi in;
 Zie chun na Lal sakmel tuibang tawm lai'
 Chun nem silhpuon hui in va mun la.</lyrics>
</song>